quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,101,"E ko honno njeddirton nde tawnoo Aayeeje Alla …óen no janngeede e dow moo…óon, Nulaa…óo Makko on kadi no hakkunde mo'on? Kala on moolii…óo e Alla, gom…óii o fewnaama e laawol foccii ngol."
  3,102,"Hey mon gom…óim…ďe, kuliree Alla no O Haaniri hulireede, wata on maayu dey, si wanaa hara ko on jebbilii…ďe."
  3,103,"Jogitee …ďoggol Alla ngol on denndaangal, wata on certu. JaŇčto…óon dokkeAlla on e dow moo…óon nde laatino…óon ayru…ďe, O Woowindiri hakkunde …ďer…óe mon …óen woŇčtir…óon e dokke Makko koo on musi…ó…ďe; on laatioke e tonndu ngayka yiite, O Da…óndi on e magge. ko wano nii Alla ∆ĀannginiraŇčta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, bela jo'o, on feeway."
  3,104,"Yo laato e moo…óon mofte : noddooje e mo∆ī∆īere, yamiroo…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi ha…óoo…ďe ko a√Īinii. Ko …ďen …óon ngoni malaa…ďe …ďen."
  3,105,"Wata on laato hona …ďen sertu…ďe lurri …ďaawo nde laa…ďtu…ói…óin ari e ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āen …óon, no woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe."
  3,106,"√Ďande jeece rawnata geece goo …ďawla. Si ko …ďen …ďe jeece mu'un …ďawli : "e on yeddu …ďaawo gom…óinal mon? Mee…óiree lepte …óen sabu ko laatino…óon hi…óon njedda"."
  3,107,"Si tawii ko …ďeen …ďe jeece mun ndanwni, …ďe ngonii e ndeer Yurmeende Alla, kam…ďe ko …ďe saasoo…ďe toon."
  3,108,"∆äee …óoo, ko Aayeeje Alla, Mi…óen Janngira …óe e dow maa…óa e goonga. Alla wonaani muuyoowo too√Īde e winndere he."